OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRed Arrows in 'special     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmeasures' over harassment  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Red Arrows display team is in      
OL,6, "special measures" after a report found
OL,7, predatory behaviour towards women was  
OL,8, "widespread and normalised".           
OL,10,FA recent investigation described a     
OL,11,F"toxic culture" where women suffered   
OL,12,Fsexual harassment and bullying.        
OL,14,FDefence minister Andrew Murrison said  
OL,15,Fthere had been changes in leadership   
OL,16,Fand the team, based at RAF Waddington, 
OL,17,Fwas being closely monitored.           
OL,19,FThe RAF's chief of air staff previously
OL,20,Fsaid he was appalled by the findings.  
